<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="An error occurred on the Starex Grievance System.">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/65/Starex_University_logo.png">
<title>Error - Starex Grievance System</title>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container text-center py-5" role="main" style="max-width: 600px; margin-top: 10vh;">
    
    <div class="logo-wrapper mb-4">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/65/Starex_University_logo.png" alt="Starex University Logo" class="university-logo" style="height: 70px;">
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="display-3 font-weight-bold text-danger mb-3" style="font-weight: 800;"><%= statusCode %></h1>
    
    <h3 class="mb-4 text-dark" style="font-weight: 600;"><%= message %></h3>
    
    <p class="text-muted mb-5">Something went wrong while processing your request. If this continues to happen, please reach out to the university IT desk or try again.</p>
    
    <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-8 mx-auto">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary" aria-label="Go Back to Grievance Form">
            Return to Home
        </a>
    </div>

</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
